        <mxCell id="85" parent="25" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f0f8;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;" value="&lt;b&gt;Resiliencia (Resilience4j)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:8px&quot;&gt;🔹 Bulkhead (Auth→Identity): semáforo, max 5 concurrentes&lt;br&gt;🔹 Circuit Breaker (Dashboard→Promotion): 10-window, 50% fail, 5s open&lt;br&gt;🔹 Retry (Notification): 3 attempts, 2s backoff · Async parallel dispatch&lt;br&gt;🔹 Cache-Aside (Promotion): Caffeine L2 + Redis · QR cache (Gateway→Redis)&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="70" width="630" x="30" y="440" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="86" parent="25" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0f8f0;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;" value="&lt;b&gt;Privacidad &amp;amp; Compliance (FERPA)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:8px&quot;&gt;🔹 FERPA: identidad real solo en Identity Vault (SHA-256 salted)&lt;br&gt;🔹 K-Anonymity (Dashboard): enmascara grupos &amp;lt; 5&lt;br&gt;🔹 14-day TTL: aristas de contacto se purgan automáticamente&lt;br&gt;🔹 Audit trail: todos los accesos a identidad emiten eventos Kafka&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="70" width="630" x="690" y="440" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="87" parent="25" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#eef4fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;" value="&lt;b&gt;Testing Strategy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:8px&quot;&gt;✅ Unit/Integration: JUnit 5 + Testcontainers (8 servicios, ~270+ tests)&lt;br&gt;✅ E2E (bloqueante PROD): port-forward contra Stage AKS + Gradle&lt;br&gt;✅ Performance: Locust (API endpoints)&lt;br&gt;✅ Security: OWASP ZAP (escaneo de vulnerabilidades)&lt;br&gt;✅ Coverage: JaCoCo &amp;ge; 70% instruction coverage&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
